import {Container, Content, Row} from "./styles"
import Button from "./componentes/Button";
import Input from "./componentes/Input/Input";
import { useState } from "react";


const  App = () => {

  const [CurrentNumber, setCurrentNumber] = useState(0);

  const HandleNumber = (num) => {

    setCurrentNumber (prev => `${num}${prev}`)
  }
 
  return (
    <Container >
      <Content>
        <Input/>
        <Row>
          <Button label="7" onClick={HandleNumber(7)} />
          <Button label="8"/>
          <Button label="9"/>
          <Button label="x"/>
        </Row>
        <Row>
          <Button label="4" />
          <Button label="5"/>
          <Button label="6"/>
          <Button label={"-"}/>
        </Row>
        <Row>
          <Button label="1" />
          <Button label="2"/>
          <Button label="3"/>
          <Button label={"+"}/>
        </Row>
        <Row>
          <Button label={"C"} />
          <Button label="0"/>
          <Button label={"."}/>
          <Button label={"="}/>
        </Row>
        
        
      </Content> 
    
    </Container>   
   
  );
}

export default App;
